reviews.review_text: Best Version This is the best recording of this show that I could find in the archive.  Awesome!

" I wonder how many of you were watching TV last night" Very nice sound here..The fall of 85' was ever so sweet and the Fox shows are a prime example. Solid from start to finish..so please..GIVE IT A WHIRL>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!!
